text: Blair Marshall Tickner was born 13 October 1993 in Napier. He is a New Zealand cricketer who played two One Day Internationals and 8 Twenty20 Internationals for New Zealand. He is set to take over the bowling attack once Neil Wagner retires from international cricket. ==Other websites== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand cricketers Category:Sportspeople from North Island Category:People from Napier, New Zealand
